This is the World English Bible, a project to create a modern
translation of the Bible free of copyrights and archaic language. Based
on the [American Standard Version](../asv/index.md), the Greek Majority
Text, and the Hebrew Biblia Hebraica Stuttgartensia. The WEB includes
the Apocrypha. This text, published in 2000, is in the public domain by
explicit donation.

